sub_title: Teacher/ Lecturer     ( MEd specialized in Education Management, BSc., CELTA, BTEC Level 5)
summary: Experienced English Language teacher with a passion for Teaching.  Comfortable in teaching both local the Cambridge syllabus.  In addition, I have been a part time English Language lecturer at several higher education institutes. Skilled in Teaching English as a Second Language, Education Management, Teacher Training and Counselling. Strong education professional with a Master of Education specialized in Education Management, CELTA, Pearson BTEC Level 5 Advance Teaching Diploma, and many more related qualifications.
